{"tid":1956522,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"新詩創作","createTime":"2020-04-03T08:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T09:28:30.000Z","uid":326967,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1963bc23d5d74e46ddedda90cf8b6f1d3d463edd","tid":1956522,"uid":326967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:37:00.000Z","msg":"《凡是醜惡》 青山多變幻<br />\n<br />\n凡是醜惡的我都記著<br />\n牠們堆滿在絕望的山岭上<br />\n遙遙望去，陣陣腥臭味吹向我<br />\n腐爛的身軀早已動彈不得<br />\n等著我的是成為麻木不仁<br />\n將成為另一座山上的渺小<br />\n而一切將回歸虛無<br />\n似不曾存在過<br />\n似等待著下一個靈魂"},{"pid":"5d761d7ab6373a9d050bfec20992977f152353f6","tid":1956522,"uid":247104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:56:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"52f74da1e80de4f41009d28ac3289f0cf248ad56","tid":1956522,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:28:30.000Z","msg":"上一首正啲"}]}